{"tid":2081949,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"招魂認母 - 李碧華","createTime":"2020-06-27T15:33:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-02T10:59:17.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"6403b455d6c9e8abb06e52718c80cc4631cee08c","tid":2081949,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T15:33:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9D%8E%E7%A2%A7%E8%8F%AF/daily/article/20200627/20944833/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E7%25A2%25A7%25E8%258F%25AF%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200627%2F20944833%2F&d=mwjAj24IHyfJiBWsHz9aFpLdSN32AczdJcE5lfwVwJ8%3D&h=645b8b67\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E7%25A2%25A7%25E8%258F%25AF%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200627%2F20944833%2F&h=7d54d43a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9D%8E%E7%A2%A7%E8%8F%AF/daily/article/20200627/20944833/</a><br />\n<br />\n招魂認母 - 李碧華<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20200627/large/1593149670_b35b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20200627%2Flarge%2F1593149670_b35b.jpg&h=b3108599&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n去年9月底，15歲女生赤裸浮屍離奇出現在海面，警方指死因無可疑，且極速火化不留追查痕跡。死因裁判法庭近日就案件作研訊前檢討。<br />\n<br />\n死者是游泳健將陳彥霖，「自殺」抑「被自殺」一直充滿疑團。女兒失蹤，義助尋人的子明哥，在奔波期內知悉她死訊傳出，一夜之間與彥霖母親和舅父失去聯絡，兩位親人人間蒸發&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n彥霖曾多次參加反送中運動，花樣少女不明不白化作青灰，此後亦不少年輕人在示威抗爭中消失了，被送中被殺被自殺，成為空中飛人（落地無血）和海上浮屍，公安黑警暴行被包庇姑息，竟逍遙法外？為堵悠悠眾口，TVB新聞總監出馬做了陳母訪問，蒙面效果假得很；之後<br />\n。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n所以最好是包公審烏盆般招魂，一如Hello Kitty藏屍案開審時，法庭上所有光管不斷閃動，那被煮半熟的人頭自己申冤。亡魂庭上哭喊一聲：「媽！」，我們就信了。 <br />\n<br />\n李碧華<br />\n電郵 :mcwriter@appledaily.com"},{"pid":"107dfd71af3c00fd091ca94a6a1f7ec5f14d77c4","tid":2081949,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T10:52:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9D%8E%E7%A2%A7%E8%8F%AF/daily/article/20200702/20947721/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E7%25A2%25A7%25E8%258F%25AF%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200702%2F20947721%2F&d=mwjAj24IHyfJiBWsHz9aFpLdSN32AczdJcE5lfwVwJ8%3D&h=e49bc108\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E7%25A2%25A7%25E8%258F%25AF%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200702%2F20947721%2F&h=36426d98\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9D%8E%E7%A2%A7%E8%8F%AF/daily/article/20200702/20947721/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n口紅妖（下） - 李碧華<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20200702/large/1593584895_147b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20200702%2Flarge%2F1593584895_147b.jpg&h=13adb58b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n由中層主管爬上高層、最高層，是金字塔之路。<br />\n<br />\n工作很累，有時午<br />\n。。。。。。<br />\n本就不討喜，怎能肩負重任？<br />\n<br />\n當她掏出那潘<br />\n。。。。。。<br />\n──就像上電，連人也好看點。<br />\n<br />\n是的，這是<br />\n。。。。。。<br />\n只是「藍蘋」。<br />\n<br />\n「。。。。。。」<br />\n<br />\n每回她元氣大傷又腹背受敵時，只消塗上這詭異的口紅，就換來一段時間的攀爬上進，贏得位高權重之驕傲，付出代價包括友情、親情、愛情和人緣──沒有朋友，六親緣薄，僅有的窩囊丈夫也受不了離婚了，子女隨父，而且在大機構中無一下屬信服只在淫威下陽奉陰違&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n殘餘的口紅快用完待添了，只能省着挖出來刮出來，薄薄塗一層──瞅着自己像個等待毒品的道姑，臉容扭曲肌肉抽搐，嘴唇乾澀而且思考能力遲鈍，一個字：「殘」！<br />\n<br />\n口紅妖出現時，林莎莉以為又可議價續期，提出僅存之籌碼：<br />\n<br />\n「我已付出生命中珍貴的東西了，怎能臨尾斷供？我還有高價的『尊嚴』&hellip;&hellip;」<br />\n<br />\n「哈哈哈！」口紅妖笑：「這東西最不值錢了！而且你一早已失掉，竟然不曉得？」<br />\n<br />\n丹祺口紅隨妖他去。永遠另有買家。（完） <br />\n<br />\n李碧華<br />\n電郵 :mcwriter@appledaily.com"},{"pid":"6f18dee2aa43d668a12f0852a160c47fae3f5168","tid":2081949,"uid":237562,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T10:59:17.000Z","msg":"舉頭三呎有神明<br />\n<br />\n害死人嘅自己因住"}]}